OL,5,G1100 Dogs Behaving (Very) Badly
OL,6,G     Australia
OL,7,     FCan Graeme Hall restore harmony
OL,8,     Fafter Pomeranian-cross Leo bites a
OL,9,     Fhand that feeds? And Mel is at her
OL,10,     Fwits' end with her Schnauzers'
OL,11,     Fimpact on her canine couture
OL,12,     Fbusiness.
OL,13,G1200 Dogs Behaving (Very) Badly
OL,14,G     Australia
OL,15,     FAfter being hit by a van at just
OL,16,     F12 weeks old, Mini Fox Terrier
OL,17,     FRomulus becomes aggressive when
OL,18,     Fher owners show affection towards
OL,19,     Feach other. Can Graeme Hall
OL,20,     Fintervene?
