OL,6,     FA speeding murder suspect is
OL,7,     Fpursued through downtown Bradford,
OL,8,     Fand a speeding car thief picks a
OL,9,     Ffight with a tree.
OL,10,G1700 Police Interceptors
OL,11,     FA runaway mugger rams Faulko off
OL,12,     Fthe road and puts him in hospital.
OL,13,     FThe team hunts down the driver
OL,14,     Fresponsible. Meanwhile Liam locks
OL,15,     Fup a rogue biker.
OL,16,G1800 Police Interceptors
OL,17,     FSpike breaks out a drug wipe for a
OL,18,     Fteenage tearaway on two wheels,
OL,19,     Fbut will the biker heed his dad's
OL,20,     Fwise words?
