OL,5,G1900 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FChris's tracker dog Ronny has a
OL,7,     Ftwitchy nose but will this canine
OL,8,     Fcrime fighter manage to track down
OL,9,     Fa villain?
OL,10,G2000 Police Interceptors
OL,11,     FThe interceptors make an early
OL,12,     Fhour dash to catch a team of late
OL,13,     Fnight burglars and one of the
OL,14,     Fsuspects treats Liam to a face
OL,15,     Ffull of saliva.
OL,16,G2100 Trauma Room One
OL,17,     FAfter collapsing at the wheel of
OL,18,     Fhis car, a stroke victim's brain
OL,19,     Fis swelling and scans reveal a
OL,20,     Ftumour which needs removing. Plus
OL,21,     Fa delicate spinal operator to
OL,22,     Falleviate lower back pain. (Ep2)
