OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FTwenty-one-year-old Ryan loses his
OL,7,     Fhelmet and suffers serious
OL,8,     Finjuries after a motorcycle
OL,9,     Faccident, and a toddler suffers a
OL,10,     Fseizure so severe he's placed in
OL,11,     Fan induced coma.
OL,12,G2300 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,13,     FA 41-year-old man is thrown 10
OL,14,     Ffeet in the air after a motorbike
OL,15,     Faccident, leaving him critically
OL,16,     Finjured. A five-year-old girl
OL,17,     Fsuffers a terrifying seizure,
OL,18,     Fpossibly caused by sepsis.
