OL,5,G0000 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FSecurity are called when a patient
OL,7,     Fis abusive to the nurses and
OL,8,     Fdoctors and Emma arrives by air
OL,9,     Fambulance after falling 30 feet
OL,10,     Foff a castle wall.
OL,11,G0100 #Text Me When You Get Home
OL,12,     FIn 2014, estate agent Beverly
OL,13,     FCarter was kidnapped and killed
OL,14,     Fwhile showing a home to a person
OL,15,     Fshe believed was a potential
OL,16,     Fbuyer. Detectives used phone data
OL,17,     Fto help find her body.
